<p begin="24350000t" end="39020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40040000t" end="73370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74400000t" end="139700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260920000t" end="304610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="305630000t" end="371960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="415740000t" end="495040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="517180000t" end="531850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532860000t" end="566190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="567230000t" end="618880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619950000t" end="669320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670330000t" end="729030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="801460000t" end="831380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第7話 陰天&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="907570000t" end="928840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;無論推理的過程如何&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="929920000t" end="952900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;這個女人所掌握的,的確是事實&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="963960000t" end="987280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;如果這個消息透露給警方&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="988320000t" end="1027000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;警方很快就會得出&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;KIRA就是夜神月的結論&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1036360000t" end="1048300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;只能把她除掉了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1060050000t" end="1068690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;怎麼了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1092420000t" end="1100380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;沒什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1121120000t" end="1152750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;重新整理過你剛說的話後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1159150000t" end="1186450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;我覺得應該盡快&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;沿著這條線索開始調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1198190000t" end="1210810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;真的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1211870000t" end="1222450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1223550000t" end="1244480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;這件事你還有跟其他人說過嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1245570000t" end="1267870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;還沒,你是第一個&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1287610000t" end="1298870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;太好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1299960000t" end="1317930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;不過你要怎麼除掉她?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1318980000t" end="1341280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;總不能馬上在這裡動手吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1342340000t" end="1364290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;這用不著路克來提醒&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1365360000t" end="1377980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;我自有辦法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1392720000t" end="1403640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;這麼光明正大啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1410400000t" end="1443390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;能告訴我那起公車劫持案&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;發生的日期和時間嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1450440000t" end="1465680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;12月20日&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1466790000t" end="1512070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;在朝顏丘前&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;11:02分前往太空樂園的班車&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1525520000t" end="1543490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;12月20日&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1552210000t" end="1582130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;開往太空樂園對吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1583240000t" end="1592220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1608270000t" end="1622600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;(間木照子自殺)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1623620000t" end="1644550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;(2007年1月1日下午1點15分)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1645640000t" end="1667590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;(盡量想一個不會給別人添麻煩)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1668660000t" end="1686970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;(又不會被發現屍體的死法)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1688010000t" end="1708940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;這樣遺體就不會很快被發現&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1715710000t" end="1732660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;就算被找到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1733730000t" end="1760690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;也有未婚夫死了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這個最佳的自殺原因&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1792120000t" end="1818400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;路克,有什麼事這麼好笑嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1874200000t" end="1909120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;很抱歉逐一盤問各位&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1918910000t" end="1937910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;KIRA並不在你們當中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1962960000t" end="1971260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1972300000t" end="1993570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;你為什麼會斷定沒有?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1998320000t" end="2022320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;其實我早就準備好陷阱&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2023350000t" end="2050310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;用來確定對方是不是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2059050000t" end="2089310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;不過對你們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我還不需要動用到它&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2127790000t" end="2137460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;我接個電話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2173830000t" end="2202160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;叫我們關掉手機,自己卻沒關&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2210870000t" end="2240560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;知道了,我這邊也剛結束&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2241570000t" end="2258180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;你自己用鑰匙進來吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2280270000t" end="2291190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;渡要來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2312970000t" end="2321950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;我明白了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2330320000t" end="2346240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;如果你不介意的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2347340000t" end="2361670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;這件事就由我來轉達吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2362690000t" end="2374630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;不了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2375700000t" end="2405960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;可以的話,我想當面跟他說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2407070000t" end="2420720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;聽完你的意見之後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2421750000t" end="2444730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;我覺得應該盡快告訴他們&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2469460000t" end="2478440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;也對&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2516180000t" end="2538480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;還有10秒就要1點15分了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2552880000t" end="2587800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;真想看看這個女人是怎麼死的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2588910000t" end="2607220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;但是又不能跟上去&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2639300000t" end="2660570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;好了,快去死吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2800790000t" end="2823430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;KIRA…一定會被逮捕吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2892220000t" end="2903820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;怎麼回事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2904900000t" end="2918890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;時間已經過了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2956620000t" end="2970950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;好奇怪&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2971960000t" end="2987540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;為什麼這個女人不行動呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3000990000t" end="3026590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;明明已經用犯人做過測試了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3027690000t" end="3047370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;「自殺」這個死因是可以生效的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3048370000t" end="3059290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;只要寫上去&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3060390000t" end="3080980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;就會依照時間上吊自殺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3089750000t" end="3116370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;而且死亡過程&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也是在有效的範圍內&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3117440000t" end="3132680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;這我也檢驗過好幾次了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3150480000t" end="3159460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;那為什麼…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3221880000t" end="3230520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;路克…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3238560000t" end="3272920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;他在我寫筆記本的時候&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;笑得很詭異&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3280610000t" end="3294600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;不僅如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3295620000t" end="3324630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;剛剛問名字的時候他也很奇怪&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3334660000t" end="3356960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;都是和名字有關的時候…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3370700000t" end="3378660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;假名?&#x202c;</p>
